modShortDescription: This mod adds screamer zombies to more spawn groups.
modDescription:
This mod adds screamer [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) to more spawn groups.

## Details

* Still WIP. Currently adds screamers to every spawn group. This seems to generate a few screamers per avg. or larger POI.
* Need to tune more.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/doughphunghus/7D2D-Doughs-Mods-a19/tree/main/Doughs-Screamers-Spawn-More)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/17197-doughs-modlets/).
